'''Authority Currency Exchanges''' were locations where one could convert non-standard commodities or currencies into [[Authority Cash Voucher]]s in the [[Corporate Sector/Legends|Corporate Sector]] in the years preceding the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. Users would trade [[Crystalline vertex/Legends|crystalline vertex]], gems, precious metals, ore, and obscure currencies, and the exchange would issue an Authority Cash Voucher for the value, minus a small percentage as processing fee. Authority Currency Exchanges were usually staffed lightly with disbursements [[auto-clerk]]s doing the actual counting and issuing.

